{"tid":1453901,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[皇家香港軍團］偽裝成對方人員，被捕後可即場槍決 !","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T05:54:40.000Z","uid":288912,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d45b415ee5c965ec2ca19f46b6bf6fd535c83eb6","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:39:12.000Z","msg":"1944年12月16日，盟軍登陸諾曼第後向德國逐步進逼，<span style=\"color: red;\">希特拉</span>將所有兵力集中在比利時亞登地區，孤注一擲發動絕地反擊，展開突出部之役(Battle of Bulge)，並且派出由奧托.史科尼兹率領的一支受過特別訓練，並且能講流利美式英語的約160人特種部隊，穿上由戰俘身上獲得的美軍制服，裝備，武器及車輛，<span style=\"color: red;\">假扮成美軍</span>，進行麒麟作戰(Operation Greif)。<br />\n<br />\n德軍特種部隊滲透到美軍後方，更改路標，制做混亂，誤導及趁機殺害毫無防範之小單位美軍。又佔據繆斯河上之橋樑，保障德軍進攻通道無阻，其後德軍反攻被盟軍瓦解，部隊遭到重創，損失約10萬兵員。<br />\n<br />\n而被捕德軍特種部隊成員由於<span style=\"color: red;\">身穿美軍軍服，不受日內瓦國際公約保護，兼且觸犯戰爭罪行</span>，被美軍指揮官命令憲兵<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即場執行槍決</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/712822242120609/posts/2436536723082477?s=747931118&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F712822242120609%2Fposts%2F2436536723082477%3Fs%3D747931118%26sfns%3Dmo&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=38179cef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/712822242120609/posts/2436536723082477?s=747931118&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"01e9f3b5edf63154d51e7eb26f76b91fe3871189","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:39:24.000Z","msg":"以"},{"pid":"d86374351333598161c4d026d82e98e0bd286916","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:39:37.000Z","msg":"武"},{"pid":"865a9910dd027d2500f0b2ef1c221a9c887ff9ec","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"制"},{"pid":"05a9b5458add0e6b23930be3f2441fe5d224d7fc","tid":1453901,"uid":209967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:40:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5c23d96d2b135e2bd82049f422ed7517e449014","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:41:03.000Z","msg":"暴"},{"pid":"ac18a3f9f79d8d155cb70da9b0ab3367bbee289d","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:41:16.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"839914ef519117e7e56503270f4fcb44d0806d8b","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:41:28.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"4e5c0fdd792213f5f316f48df936f1bd5bc2fbb5","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:41:40.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"6990a658ec4f628f385d95dd746750657d646bcf","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:41:51.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"4036a2bacc997e1bd17f3a745c65a55e10fd68cf","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:42:30.000Z","msg":"建"},{"pid":"2df699b673711fa096e411f1118b7be407a447f7","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:42:41.000Z","msg":"立"},{"pid":"2b0557aaee334e410ab17843bc7bc5efe0c83a80","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:42:52.000Z","msg":"自"},{"pid":"cb54ec772375a475468b4f8fb76eb4e5721215bd","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:43:04.000Z","msg":"衛"},{"pid":"224291ef4e08e738ebacd3f598a5b577dc1e8ac2","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:43:14.000Z","msg":"武"},{"pid":"96bf62bbf40080fdf28858e7d8a4b94d9cdd6222","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:43:26.000Z","msg":"力"},{"pid":"69125acbaafe25afe4cf858f1ad6963a2491ca44","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:43:36.000Z","msg":"以武制暴"},{"pid":"eb944a9c68277d8f3be0a4fca705a7162a58ee7a","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:43:47.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"c6974608b6632d9f9decd38cfd00097b0aca3e45","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:44:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建立自衛武力</span>"},{"pid":"cb65af6709899f95c140ab1890e0f141cc638991","tid":1453901,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:45:36.000Z","msg":"發夢見到扮示威者既狗cap住黎打就岩啦"},{"pid":"cad38ad3175d16198b13ba3ceea8f0cb275bca72","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:45:55.000Z","msg":"香港法例第221章第101條<br />\n<br />\n(2)<span style=\"color: red;\">任何人</span>可無需手令而逮捕任何他合理地懷疑犯了可逮捕的罪行的人。 (由1967年第70號第2條代替)"},{"pid":"2e7f5059ddc437281beeba391b371a57a2572d54","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:46:26.000Z","msg":"香港法例第221章第101條<br />\n<br />\n(4)任何人如發現任何人管有任何他有合理理由懷疑該人是<span style=\"color: red;\">藉可逮捕的罪行而取得的財產</span>，可無需手令而逮捕最後述及的人，並取得該財產的管有。 (由1967年第70號第2條修訂)"},{"pid":"ed731e58b13f30007921b7d9e8f5085b814c143d","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:47:07.000Z","msg":"香港法例第221章第101條<br />\n<br />\n(5)根據載於此的任何條文逮捕任何人的每一人(如作出逮捕的人本身不是警務人員)，須將如此逮捕的人及他已取得管有的財產(如有的話)交付警務人員，以便在合理的範圍內盡快將該人帶到裁判官席前，以待裁判官按照法律處理，或為該目的而<span style=\"color: red;\">親自在合理的範圍內盡快將該人帶到裁判官席前</span>。 (由1911年第51號修訂；由1912年第2號附表修訂)"},{"pid":"7e779a880452243dcdb0927c3de15efeb137ab08","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"香港法例第221章第101A條<br />\n<br />\n1)任何人於防止罪案時或於進行或協助合法逮捕罪犯或疑犯或非法地不在羈留中的人時，可使用就<span style=\"color: red;\">當時環境而言屬於合理的武力</span>。"},{"pid":"3d878243e9745bf84f77f0afb1e52e4fe9e54e8d","tid":1453901,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb65af6709899f95c140ab1890e0f141cc638991","tid":1453901,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:45:36.000Z","msg":"發夢見到扮示威者既狗cap住黎打就岩啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"用221章101A條（1）打狗，用221章101條（5）直接押佢去法院"}]}